@startuml
title 状态面与事件面边界
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "Onboard / Vehicle Side" #F8F8F8 {
  rectangle "状态采样器" as sampler #D5E8D4
  rectangle "事件检测器" as detector #FCE5CD
  rectangle "Bulk Producer" as producer #E8F3FF
}

package "Ground Station Side" #F8F8F8 {
  rectangle "StateSubscriber" as sub_state #D5E8D4
  rectangle "EventSubscriber" as sub_event #FCE5CD
  rectangle "Bulk Consumer" as sub_bulk #E8F3FF
}

sampler --> sub_state : StateSnapshot.VehicleCore\n周期 / 可覆盖 / 最新值
detector --> sub_event : StateEvent.VehicleEvent\n离散 / 稀疏 / 关键变化
producer --> sub_bulk : BulkChannelDescriptor\n主协议发现，旁路传输内容

note bottom of sampler
快照不应承载一次性告警文本
end note

note bottom of detector
事件不应用来重建完整姿态状态
end note
@enduml
